(In reply to roberthuff from comment #15)

Hi, I'm the reporter. If this is holding up other updates, have you tried commenting out 

PKG_PLUGINS_DIR = "/usr/local/lib/pkg/";
PKG_ENABLE_PLUGINS = true;
PLUGINS [ provides ];

from /usr/local/etc/pkg.conf

and then running pkg update -f

and then running pkg upgrade, as a temporary workaround? This is what I've done.
